data.description: Welcome to this exquisite home, a true gem with a breathtaking cream and white facade that exudes timeless elegance. Nestled in a prime location near Denman Estate Park and the bustling Medical Center, this residence offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Step inside to concrete flooring and discover a spacious interior flooded with natural light, thanks to its high ceilings and strategically placed windows. The bamboo stairs lead and continue throughout the second floor to the other three bedrooms and three bathrooms, providing ample space for a growing household or guests with a cedar closet in the primary. The living room, complete with a cozy fireplace, is an inviting space to gather and create cherished memories. Emphasizing ease and comfort, this home boasts low maintenance with no landscaping requirements and no carpet throughout. Whether you have a busy lifestyle or simply want to enjoy your free time to the fullest, this residence ensures a stress-free living experience. Perfectly situated with easy access to major highways, this home epitomizes city living at its best. Indulge in the nearby cultural attractions, dining options, and entertainment venues, all within reach. Make this dream home your reality and embrace the epitome of sophisticated living. Schedule your private tour today and embark on the next chapter of your life!
